JPN\">{{cite web | title = Japanese chart positions | url = http://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/artist/51059/ranking/cd_album/ | website =[[Oricon|Oricon Style]]|accessdate=16 October 2012}}</ref>\n| 8\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[Recording Industry Association of New Zealand|New Zealand Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"nz\">{{cite web|url=http://charts.nz/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Oasis|title=New Zealand Charts > Oasis|website=charts.nz|accessdate=1 June 2019}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[VG-lista|Norwegian Albums Chart]]<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://norwegiancharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Oasis&titel=%28What%27s+The+Story%29+Morning+Glory%3F&cat=a |website=norwegiancharts.com | publisher = Hung Medien | accessdate =9 June 2012 | title = VG-Lista \u2013 Oasis \u2013 (What's the Story) Morning Glory? (album)}}</ref>\n| 5\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Fonogr\u00e1fica Portuguesa|Portuguese Albums Chart]]<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=rQkEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA81#v=onepage&q&f=false  | work = [[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] | accessdate =27 June 2012 | title = Hits of the World \u2013 Portugal | page = 81 | date = 8 June 1996| publisher = Nielsen Business Media }}</ref>\n| 6\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a|Spanish Albums Chart]]<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=iQ8EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA48#v=onepage&q&f=false  | work = [[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] | accessdate =9 June 2012 | title = Hits of the World \u2013 Spain | page = 48 | date = 23 March 1996| publisher = Nielsen Business Media }}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[Sverigetopplistan|Swedish Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"swe\">{{cite web|url=http://swedishcharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Oasis|title=Swedish Charts > Oasis|website=swedishcharts.com |accessdate=2 September 2008| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080925152829/http://swedishcharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Oasis| archivedate= 25 September 2008<!--Added by DASH