80925152829/http://swedishcharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Oasis| archivedate= 25 September 2008<!--Added by DASHBot-->}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[Swiss Music Charts|Swiss Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"swi\">{{cite web|url=http://hitparade.ch/artist/Oasis|title=Swiss Charts > Oasis|website=hitparade.ch |accessdate=24 September 2011}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[UK Albums Chart]]<ref>{{Cite web | url =http://www.officialcharts.com/search/albums/what's-the-story-morning-glory/ | website = theofficialcharts.com | accessdate = 9 June 2012 | title= what's the story morning glory}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|US [[Billboard 200|''Billboard'' 200]]<ref name=\"allmusic charts\">\"[https://www.billboard.com/music/oasis/chart-history/billboard-200 Oasis Chart History: Billboard 200]\". ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]''. Retrieved 1 June 2019.</ref>\n| 4\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[List of record charts|Zimbabwean Albums Chart]]<ref>* Zimbabwe. Kimberley, C. ''Zimbabwe: albums chart book''. Harare: C. Kimberley, 2000</ref>\n| 5\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Year-end charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! Chart (1995)\n! Position\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Belgian Albums Chart (Flanders)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/annual.asp?year=1995&cat=a|title=Jaaroverzichten 1995|work=Ultratop 50 |publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=2011-04-02|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n|84\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Belgian Albums Chart (Wallonia)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ultratop.be/fr/annual.asp?year=1995&cat=a|title=Rapports annuels 1995|work=Ultratop 50 |publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=2011-04-02|language=French}}</ref>\n|63\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|UK Albums (OCC)<ref name=\"every\">{{cite web|url=http://www.everyhit.com/chartalb5.html|title=Chart Archive - 1990s Albums|website=everyHit.com|accessdate=28 July 2014}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|2\n|-\n! Chart (1996)\n! Position\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Australian Albums (ARIA)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://aria.com.au